metadata.name: An intro
metadata.description:
Fluid universe why? Because
I have started liking things in motion,
Maybe cause there's so much of me in motion,
Everything happened so fast, by the time I realised it,
It was over and people were in motion,
I kept holding on,
But everyone else was in motion,
I still kept holding on,
Just looking at people in motion,
Somedays it broke my heart,
I tried to be in sync with other people's motion,
But I couldn't do it,
I lost myself,
And in search of myself,
I started being in motion,
Running, jumping, exploring,
Just to find myself,
That's why I like motion cause,
That is the only way I can find myself.
